speech.p: I am sorry but I will not; I am just finishing.

One of my heroes of the yearthere may be many other candidatesis an entrepreneur called Julian Richards, who is now coming up to retirement and is handing over 40% of his company, Richer Sounds, to the employees, ensuring that they have a stake in the future. We need more incentives like that to promote loyalty and give people a real stake in their future. I thoroughly support the Queens Speech.
